# Make all
all: nothing hello ascii squareFunc

# Make clean
clean :
	rm -rf *.o nothing hello intPtr void1 void2 void3 void4 helloVoid char1 char2 char3 char4 helloChar array1 array2 array3 array4 helloArray helloArray2 helloArray3
